Global Petrol Outboard Motor Market Insights
Petrol Outboard Motor Market size was valued at USD 3.8 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.9% from 2024 to 2030.

Petrol Outboard Motor Market Overview
The global petrol outboard motor market was valued at USD 4.25 billion in 2024 and is projected to expand at a CAGR of 4.6% during the forecast period. The increasing popularity of recreational boating, coupled with a rise in demand for efficient and powerful outboard motors, is driving the market's growth. Technological advancements in fuel efficiency and performance enhancements are expected to further propel the market. Furthermore, the increasing adoption of outboard motors for commercial fishing and marine transportation in developing economies is likely to boost market dynamics. As the global boating industry continues to grow, the petrol outboard motor market is positioned for robust expansion.

